OL,3,CMiniature masterpieces: Model railway
OL,4,Cexhibition welcomes thousands of
OL,5,Cvisitors
OL,7,FThe organisers of a model railway
OL,8,Fexhibition say they are hopeful the
OL,9,Fevent will return next year, after
OL,10,Fthousands of people attended this
OL,11,Fyear's convention.
OL,13,FIt is the thirteenth year of the
OL,14,Fannual Cumbria Railway Exhibition,
OL,15,Fwhich was held in Workington in West
OL,16,FCumbria on 16 and 17 November.
