OL,7,FPhilip Tuer is a volunteer at Solrail,
OL,8,Fthe Cumbrian non profit which
OL,9,Forganised the event. He says visitors
OL,10,Fhave travelled from all over the UK to
OL,11,Fattend.
OL,13,F"We've had quite a few from the
OL,14,FNortheast today, who have come across
OL,15,Fand I've seen one gentleman from
OL,16,FShropshire, quite a few from Scotland.
OL,18,F"The standard of modelling has been
OL,19,Fabsolutely phenomenal and the feedback
OL,20,Fprovided so far has been very
OL,21,Fpositive."
