OL,7,FOrganisers say they have already
OL,8,Freceived bookings for next year and
OL,9,Fbut would like to see more young
OL,10,Fpeople taking up the hobby.
OL,12,FRichard Morsley from Solrail said:
OL,13,F"Model railways are typically classed
OL,14,Fas an older man's hobby at the moment
OL,15,Fbecause of the cost and the intricacy
OL,16,Finvolved.
