OL,7,F"However, there are a lot of young
OL,8,Fmodellers coming onto the scene and it
OL,9,Fhelps that celebrities are on
OL,10,Ftelevision making them. I suppose it
OL,11,Fwas classed as a boy's toy at one time
OL,12,Fbut now it's accepted by lots of
OL,13,Fpeople as a hobby."
OL,15,FKevin Smith from Askam-In-Furness,
OL,16,FSouth Cumbria, displayed his model
OL,17,Frailway at this year's event after
OL,18,Fbuilding models became a full-time
OL,19,Fhobby since retiring two years ago.
